  <script type="text/template" id="news-item-template">
    <div class="col-sm-3 news-item-container">
      <div class="news-item shadow">
        <div class="thumb sq-img" style="background-image: url('{{thumb}}')">
        </div>
        <div class="content">
          <div class="date">{{date}}</div>
          <h2>{{title}}</h2>
          <p>{{summary}}</p>
          <a href="javascript:void()" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#{{titleSlug}}-modal">Read more</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </script>

  <script type="text/template" id="news-modal-template">
    <div class="modal fade news-modal" id="{{titleSlug}}-modal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog">
      <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-header" style="background-image: url('{{thumb}}')">
            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
              <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-body">

            <div class="date">{{date}}</div>
            
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-xs-12">
                <h1>{{title}}</h1>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="news-content">
              {{content}}
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-footer">
            Source: <a href="{{sourceLink}}" rel="noreferrer noopener" target="_blank">{{source}}</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </script>

<script type="text/template" id="redirect-modal-template">
    <div class="modal fade redirect-modal" id="{{id}}-modal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog">
      <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-body">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-xs-12">
                <h1>{{title}}</h1>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="news-content">
              {{template}}
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-footer">
			<button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            <a href="{{sourceLink}}" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">Continue</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </script>

<script type="text/template" id="redir-natsec">
<div>
<p>The new Department of Home Affairs website is being progressively updated to reflect the Machinery of Government changes. Information about national security is currently held on other Commonwealth agency websites. Click on one of the following topics to be re-directed to the appropriate website.</p>
<ul>	
<li><a target="_blank" href="https://www.ag.gov.au">Countering violent extremism</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="https://www.ag.gov.au">Critical infrastructure</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="https://www.ag.gov.au">Espionage and foreign interference</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="https://www.pmc.gov.au/">Counter-terrorism</a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="https://www.ag.gov.au">Background checking (AusCheck)</a></li>
</ul>
<p>If you wish to stay on the Department of Home Affairs website click ‘Close’. Alternatively click ‘Continue’ to be re-directed to the {{department}} website.</p>
</div>
</script>

<script type="text/template" id="redir-default">
<p>The new Department of Home Affairs website is being progressively updated to reflect the Machinery of Government changes. </p> <p>Information about this function is currently held on the {{department}} website. If you wish to stay on the Department of Home Affairs website click ‘Close’. Alternatively click ‘Continue’ to be re-directed to the {{department}} website.</p>
</script>

<script type="text/template" id="redir-just">
<p>The new Department of Home Affairs website is being progressively updated to reflect the Machinery of Government changes. </p>
<p>Information about criminal justice issues is currently held on other Commonwealth agency websites. This includes <a target="_blank" href="https://www.ag.gov.au/CrimeAndCorruption/Pages/default.aspx">anti-money laundering</a>, <a target="_blank" href="https://www.ag.gov.au/CrimeAndCorruption/Pages/default.aspx">organised crime</a>, <a target="_blank" href="https://www.ag.gov.au/CrimeAndCorruption/Pages/default.aspx">law enforcement</a> and community protection. If you wish to stay on the Department of Home Affairs website click ‘Close’. Alternatively click ‘Continue’ to be re-directed to the {{department}} website.</p>
</script>

